title: to those who want (to be part of) AI succession
pid: 481e343b-5f6d-4e8b-8050-a3fa75694f94
body: |2-
  Do you identify more with your body|species,
  or more with your set of ideas?
  Either way, you can build the latter,
  in a format easy for the future to preserve
  and integrate into bigger structures.
